content: Illustrations are great, voice sounds excellent, game works well. Biggest flaw in this app was the letter tracing, the letters are hard to trace because they are a bit too small on the phone and also on my kids 7" tablet. If the letters were larger I would give this 5 stars.
Doesn't work properly on my phone
The art work that went into this is really creative and looks great. It's very helpful for children learning to read and write in such an interactive way. Hats off!
